<TEXT>
<P>
Israeli soldiers shot and wounded at least 12 Palestinians in stone-throwing 
clashes during a general strike in the Gaza Strip and West Bank, Arab hospital 
officials said. The confrontations came as commerce and transportation ground 
to a halt in the occupied territories in the strike ordered by Muslim 
fundamentalists. 
