<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA112389-0067 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 138743 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
November 23, 1989, Thursday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 13; Column 1; Sports Desk 
</P>
