<P>
"Every day at lunch, teachers are asking for salary schedules around Los 
Angeles County. Three blocks away, a teacher is making $3,000 or $4,000 more." 
</P>
<P>
 -- David Mielke, president of ousted Culver City Federation of Teachers, about 
Culver City teachers' contract settlement. 
