<P>
Business; Part D; Page 5; Column 1; Financial Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
117 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
O.C. STOCK WATCH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Of the 100 largest publicly traded companies in Orange County, 27 gained value 
Wednesday, 25 lost and 48 remained unchanged for the day. The following chart 
shows the five biggest percentage winners and losers among county companies' 
stocks. 
</P>
