tricky? ; Photo, S.F. Ballet: Refreshingly bold stab at modern works. ; Photo, 
Jerry Seinfeld: Laughing with, not at, us. ; Photo, "Into the Woods": A musical 
with a message and even a heart, not just flash. ; Photo, Lanyer as "Cyrano": 
Summer is sweet. 
</P>
